        </div>
        <h1>Burleigh Waters, 4220 - Gold Coast</h1>
        <p class="property-subtitle">$100,000+ saved and secured within 2 weeks</p>
        <div class="hero-badge">Client Savings: Over $100,000</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Property Overview -->
    <section class="property-overview section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="overview-grid">
          <div class="overview-main">
            <h2>The Success Story</h2>
            <p class="lead-text">
              Not only did we secure this stunning family home in Burleigh within 2 weeks for our clients, but we also saved them over $100,000 within their budget. This is the power of professional buyers agent representation—speed, expertise, and substantial financial savings.
            </p>

            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h4>The Results</h4>
              <ul class="results-list">
                <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> Secured within 2 weeks</li>
                <li><strong>Savings:</strong> Over $100,000 below budget</li>
                <li><strong>Location:</strong> Burleigh Waters, one of the Gold Coast's premium family suburbs</li>
                <li><strong>Outcome:</strong> Stunning family home in highly sought-after location</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <h3>What We Did</h3>
            <ul class="success-points">
              <li>Fast-tracked property search in Burleigh Waters with precise criteria matching</li>
              <li>Identified this exceptional family home through our off-market network</li>
              <li>Conducted comprehensive market analysis to determine true property value</li>
              <li>Executed strategic negotiation saving client over $100,000</li>
              <li>Completed full due diligence including building and pest inspections</li>
              <li>Managed entire settlement process for seamless transaction within 2 weeks</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Why Burleigh Waters?</h3>
            <p>
              Burleigh Waters is one of the Gold Coast's most sought-after family suburbs. Our clients chose this location for its perfect blend of coastal proximity, excellent schools, family-friendly parks, and the iconic Burleigh lifestyle—all while being more affordable than beachfront Burleigh Heads. The suburb offers exceptional value for families seeking the Burleigh lifestyle.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="overview-sidebar">
            <div class="property-card">
              <h3>Property Details</h3>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Location:</span>
                <span class="value">Burleigh Waters, QLD 4220</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Region:</span>
                <span class="value">Gold Coast</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Property Type:</span>
                <span class="value">Family Home</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Service Type:</span>
                <span class="value">Full Buyers Agent Service</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item">
                <span class="label">Timeline:</span>
                <span class="value">2 Weeks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="detail-item savings">
                <span class="label">Client Savings:</span>
                <span class="value">$100,000+</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-card">
              <h4>Want to Save on Your Purchase?</h4>
              <p>Our expert negotiation saved this client over $100,000. See how we can help you.</p>
              <a href="/book-free-consultation" class="button-primary">Book Free Consultation</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Suburb Insights -->
    <section class="suburb-insights section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Burleigh Waters Suburb Insights</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Why Burleigh Waters offers exceptional value for families seeking the iconic Burleigh lifestyle.</p>

        <div class="insights-grid">
          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Location & Lifestyle</h3>
            <p>Minutes to world-famous Burleigh beach and James Street dining precinct. Perfect balance of coastal lifestyle and family-friendly residential atmosphere. Walk or bike to the beach.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">9/10</div>
            <h3>Family & Schools</h3>
            <p>Excellent schools including Marymount College and proximity to top primary schools. Safe, family-oriented community with multiple parks, playgrounds, and sports facilities. Perfect for raising children.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Parks & Recreation</h3>
            <p>Justins Park, multiple waterfront reserves, and easy access to Burleigh Headland National Park. Great cycling and walking paths. Tallebudgera Creek for kayaking and SUP boarding.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Value Proposition</h3>
            <p>More affordable than beachfront Burleigh Heads while offering the same lifestyle benefits. Strong capital growth potential. Excellent entry point into the prestigious Burleigh market.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">7/10</div>
            <h3>Shopping & Amenities</h3>
            <p>Close to Stockland Burleigh Heads shopping center, James Street cafés and restaurants. All amenities within easy reach. Village atmosphere with convenience.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="insight-card">
            <div class="rating">8/10</div>
            <h3>Investment Potential</h3>
            <p>Strong rental demand from families and professionals. Consistent capital growth driven by Burleigh's enduring popularity. Limited supply of quality family homes drives value.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Client Testimonial -->
    <section class="testimonial-section section">
      <div class="container-narrow">
        <div class="testimonial-feature">
          <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
          <blockquote>
            <p>Edwards & Smith not only secured this stunning family home in Burleigh within 2 weeks, but saved us over $100,000 within our budget. Their market knowledge and negotiation skills were exceptional.</p>
          </blockquote>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <p class="author-name">Edwards & Smith Client</p>
            <p class="author-title">Burleigh Waters, Gold Coast</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="faq-section section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Burleigh Waters Property Buying FAQs</h2>
        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Why choose Burleigh Waters over Burleigh Heads?</h3>
            <p>Burleigh Waters offers the same lifestyle and proximity to Burleigh beach, cafés, and amenities but at significantly better value. You get larger blocks, more family-oriented properties, and savings that can exceed $100,000+ compared to beachfront Burleigh Heads.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How did Edwards & Smith save over $100,000?</h3>
            <p>Through expert market knowledge, comprehensive property analysis, strategic negotiation, and understanding true market values. We identified the property's worth, negotiated professionally, and secured exceptional terms for our client well below their maximum budget.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Is Burleigh Waters a good family suburb?</h3>
            <p>Excellent for families. Top schools including Marymount College, safe streets, multiple parks and playgrounds, close to beaches, and a strong family-oriented community. It's one of the Gold Coast's premier family suburbs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How competitive is the Burleigh Waters market?</h3>
            <p>Highly competitive, especially for quality family homes. Properties often attract multiple buyers. Professional representation with market knowledge and negotiation expertise provides significant advantages, as demonstrated by our $100,000+ savings for this client.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Can Edwards & Smith really secure a property in 2 weeks?</h3>
            <p>Yes, when you have clear criteria, pre-approval, and expert representation. We leverage off-market opportunities, move quickly on suitable properties, and handle all due diligence efficiently. This property was secured within 2 weeks from engagement.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What's the investment potential in Burleigh Waters?</h3>
            <p>Strong fundamentals: proximity to iconic Burleigh, excellent schools, family demand, and relative affordability compared to beachfront. Historical capital growth is solid, driven by limited supply and enduring appeal of the Burleigh area.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Properties -->
    <section class="related-properties section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Other Gold Coast Properties We've Secured</h2>
        <div class="properties-grid">
          <a href="/recent-purchases/gold-coast/palm-beach-4221" class="property-card-link">
            <div class="property-card-small">
              <img src="/assets/images/palm-beach-4221-new.jpg" alt="Palm Beach property" loading="lazy" />
              <h3>Palm Beach, 4221</h3>
              <p>Perfect coastal lifestyle property</p>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="/recent-purchases/gold-coast/burleigh-heads-4220" class="property-card-link">
            <div class="property-card-small">
              <img src="/assets/images/burleigh-heads-4220-4.webp" alt="Burleigh Heads property" loading="lazy" />
              <h3>Burleigh Heads, 4220</h3>
              <p>Secured for AFL star Ben King</p>
            </div>
          </a>
